title: IAA Tonight | They Wrote Geno Off But He Didn't Write Back
description: Geno Smith and the Seahawks spoiled Russell Wilson's return to Seattle in a Monday Night thriller. Broncos first year head coach Nathaniel Hackett is under some serious fire for electing to kick a 64-yd FG instead of going for it on 4th & 5 late in the game. Brandon Marshall, LeSean McCoy, Leger Douzable and Omar Kelly discuss this and what the Cowboys should do in Dak's absence.
